flowchart TD
    A[gitpulse.sh] --> B{Which command?}

    B -->|scan| C[find_repos: scan directory]
    B -->|--help / -h| D[show_help]
    B -->|--version / -v| E[show_version]
    B -->|unknown| F[Print error]

    C --> G{Path valid?}
    G -->|no| H[Print error to stderr]
    G -->|yes| I[Loop through subdirectories]

    I --> J{Is git repo?}
    J -->|no| I
    J -->|yes| K[get_repo_status]

    K --> L{Has commits?}
    L -->|no| M[Print 'no commits' row]
    L -->|yes| N[Check dirty / clean]

    N --> O{Has upstream?}
    O -->|yes| P[Count ahead / behind]
    O -->|no| Q[Set ahead / behind = N/A]

    P --> R[Get last commit, stash, untracked]
    Q --> R
    R --> S[Print status row]

    M --> I
    S --> I